      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a 3.62 ratio limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers for precise turn-in and lateral stability. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows light road wear, the drivetrain remains tight with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A compelling driver-spec machine for the purist.",
